Package: TCRconvertR
Type: Package
Title: Convert TCR Gene Names
Description: Convert V, D, J, and/or C gene names between the 10X Genomics, 
  Adaptive 'Biotechnologies', and 'IMGT' nomenclatures. This allows for 
  T Cell Receptor ('TCR') datasets from different sequencing platforms to be combined.
Version: 1.0
